screen_desc: A mobile screen displaying a "Set location on map" interface. At the top, the time is 8:54 AM, and various status icons are visible, including notifications, Bluetooth, VPN, signal strength, Wi-Fi, and battery level. Below the location setting prompt, there is a search bar with a back arrow on the left. The on-screen keyboard is visible at the bottom, featuring a background image of a night sky with stars and a lit tent. The keyboard includes standard keys, a microphone icon, a settings icon, and a smiley face icon. The keyboard is labeled "Laban Key."

ui_elements.content_desc: "Image of a black circle with a small tail at the bottom"
